Pwd :  current directory 

Ls : files in the current directory  

Cd : navigate to another directory  

Man 'command' : a 'txt' looking screen of how to use the desired command - can be used on any commands 

'command' --help : same as the man but with extra information 

Apt -get : the application where we can download 

Apt -get update : updating the page with the applications -NEEDS to be done before installing 

Apt -get install 'program name'  : install programs 

Ifconfig : all the connections 

Iwconfig : mopde managed -> will capture packets only for our  

 

Tab autocompletes and the arrows navigate in the precious commands of the terminal 
